          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "High purity metal cobalt and manganese foils were used",
                "as targets. From ten to fourteen cobalt foils, 15 mm",
                "diameter, 0.8-1.0 g/cm2 thick, were placed in an Al",
                "target holder and interspaced with Mn foils, also",
                "15 mm diameter, 0.6-0.8 g/cm2 thick, to provide",
                "simultaneous proton bombardment.",
                "In case of cobalt targets, a stack of pellets made by",
                "compressing the necessary amount of the powdered",
                "Co-Cl(2), 15 mm diameter, 0.4-0.5 g/cm2, was also used.",
                "used. The thickness of foils and pellets was estimated",
                "by weight and area measurements."
              ]
            }
          ],
